
  <view>
    <view>
      <swiper indicator-dots="{{indicatorDots}}" autoplay="{{autoplay}}" interval="{{interval}}" duration="{{duration}}" circular="true">
        <block  wx:for="{{imgurls}}" wx:key="{{index}}">
          <swiper-item>
            <image src="{{item}}" class="swiper"/>
          </swiper-item>
        </block>
      </swiper>
    </view>
    <scroll-view scroll-x="true">
      <view class="scroll">
        <view  wx:for="{{content}}" wx:key="index" id="{{index}}" bindtap="select">
          <view class="scrollname">
            <image class="image" src="{{item.icon}}"/>
            <text style="position: absolute; top: 0;">{{item.title}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
    <view class="grayline" bindtap="content">
      <view class="userinfo">
        <image class="usericon" src="{{icon}}"/>
        <view class="username">10K</view>
      </view>
      <view style="display: flex;">
        <view class="content">
          <view class="title">时间告诉你，毕业一年后，真的有比一纸文凭更重要的东西</view>
          <view class="article">01 在我小的时候，熬夜还是一件不常见事情。那个时候身边的人的作息都十分有规律，有没有蓄意教唆人，在还不起钱的时候去像亲人朋友借钱。</view>
        </view>
        <image class="pic" src="{{pic}}"/>
      </view>
      <view>
        <view class="like">
          <image class="comment" src="{{like}}"/>
          <view style="margin-right: 0.5rem">1.5W</view>
          <image class="comment" src="{{comment}}"/>
          <view>10W</view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="border">
      <view class="serch" bindtap="serch">
        <image class="serchicon" src="{{serch}}"/>
        <view>搜索</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>